    "text": [
      "This sample project demonstrates how to use an EventBridge rule to periodically sync a Bedrock Knowledge Base data source to Amazon OpenSearch Serverless.",
      "The sample project uses an EventBridge Scheduler that runs on a regular interval. The scheduler invokes has a universal target configured to trigger the StartIngestion API on Amazon Bedrock Agent service"
